{"tid":2352552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒巴帖文重點節錄","createTime":"2021-01-04T05:54:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T06:21:03.000Z","uid":72497,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"df265b4695ae1ee7d135d7cccb51a3437fe5c8e1","tid":2352552,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:54:25.000Z","msg":"一個崩都無袋過之餘，啲支出仲係自己倒貼。重光團隊同人食飯會claim 錢，但係我兩袖清風從來無claim任何野，一個崩都無呀！<br />\n<br />\n重光團隊自己都承認全面控制1,600萬，佢地要hold錢、要推BNO，攬炒團隊同我10月已經無奈接受，由佢地。無資源就馬死落地行。<br />\n<br />\n但點L解唔問真正hold錢嘅重光做緊乜，走去屈鳩我有幾千萬洗？更何況，我地無每個月燒幾十萬落lobbying firms推BNO。"},{"pid":"a130e3b97de7c0b892bf4c51b6ab2fdc0173d752","tid":2352552,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:56:53.000Z","msg":"誓死擁護攬炒巴，大家要認清邊個先係呃人錢果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e25e552936d4310b9b86e5d201d3b55887c7b44","tid":2352552,"uid":263183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />怪錯人"},{"pid":"bb68324cf0c344a5a623a3adf356bbed6e041e27","tid":2352552,"uid":72497,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a130e3b97de7c0b892bf4c51b6ab2fdc0173d752","tid":2352552,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T05:56:53.000Z","msg":"誓死擁護攬炒巴，大家要認清邊個先係呃人錢果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T06:08:03.000Z","msg":"係，原來重光先係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3427a82fc6ef443f2e88a8b6f89594a2255fd8f","tid":2352552,"uid":187274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T06:21:03.000Z","msg":"發現插唔入攬炒巴就掉轉槍頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo